'''''Star Wars: Empire''''' was a series of comics published by [[Dark Horse Comics]]. The first issue came out on September 4, [[2002]]. It ran for 40 issues, and was continued in the [[Star Wars: Rebellion (comic series)|''Star Wars: Rebellion'']] series.

